Class LicenseAgreementDialog

java.lang.Object
  com.rrs.corona.solutionsacceleratorstudio.plugin.LicenseAgreementDialog

public final class LicenseAgreementDialog
extends java.lang.Object

LicenseAgreementDialog concerns with creating a dialog for displaying the license aggreement to the user.

The license aggrement dialog displays the license information . The dialog provides the user a way to accept or decline the license agreement.
